---
import LegalLayout from '../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
import { SITE, LEGAL } from '../consts';
---
<LegalLayout title="Accessibility Statement" description="Our commitment to making MoveWell Reviews usable for everyone.">
  <p class="lead">
    {LEGAL.entity} is committed to making {SITE.name} accessible to the widest possible audience,
    regardless of ability or technology.
  </p>

  <h2>Our standard</h2>
  <p>
    We aim to conform to the <strong>Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.1, Level AA</strong>.
    These guidelines explain how to make web content more accessible to people with a wide range of
    disabilities, including visual, auditory, motor, and cognitive.
  </p>

  <h2>What we do</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Maintain sufficient color contrast for text and interactive elements.</li>
    <li>Provide descriptive alternative text for meaningful images.</li>
    <li>Support full keyboard navigation with visible focus states.</li>
    <li>Use semantic headings and landmarks so screen readers can navigate the page.</li>
    <li>Respect the "reduce motion" setting on your device.</li>
    <li>Keep tap targets large enough to use comfortably on a phone.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Ongoing effort</h2>
  <p>
    Accessibility is an ongoing effort, and some content may not yet be fully optimized. We review the
    site regularly and fix issues as we find them.
  </p>

  <h2>Feedback</h2>
  <p>
    If you encounter an accessibility barrier on this site, please tell us so we can fix it. Email
    <a href={`mailto:${SITE.contactEmail}`}>{SITE.contactEmail}</a> with the page address and a short
    description of the problem, and we'll respond as soon as we can.
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
